[30;1m82 | [0m[35m## spy.workbooks[0m
[30;1m83 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m84 | [0m[35mIn **Seeq Server R22.0.49.00**, the ability to schedule the update of an Organizer Topic was added. [0m
[30;1m85 | [0m[35mthe internals of how Organizer Topic embedded content and date ranges are represented changed.[0m
